Assuming a C++20 compiler, what does this program print?

```cpp
#include <iostream>

template <typename T>
struct Wrap { T value; };

int main()
{
    Wrap a{ 5 };
    Wrap b{ 2.5 };
    std::cout << a.value << ' ' << b.value << '\n';
    return 0;
}
```

